Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with satellite image analysis and land cover mapping using deep learning techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end deep learning framework for data fusion. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with the retrieval of information from satellite images. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a deep learning architecture for land cover mapping. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the analysis of satellite images which can be considered as graphics.
